==================================================
Name	        : TwitterBox
version	        : 0.1
Git             : https://github.com/jayrambhia/TwitterBox
compatibility   : Linux (Ubuntu tested)

Credits : The Python-Twitter Developers for twitter library.

It's a GUI for twitter using gtk/pygtk.

To use this GUI, you need your consumer key, consumer secret, access tokey key, and access token secret.
Get all these from https://dev.twitter.com/
Enter all of the above mentioned keys in the script.

If you are behind any proxy, then enter the values accordingly.

twitterBox
	$ python twitterBox
	GUI for posting tweets and getting friends' timeline. To get friends' timeline, move your mouse arrow out of textview.

tweetBox
	$ python tweetBox
	A small widget to post tweets.
